events.message:
BIP 39: link BitcoinJS & blockchain.info implementation

BIP 39 mnemonics are featured quite prominently in the UI as well.

events.body: Semi-duplicate of https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/pull/307,  albeit,  with added `blockchain.info` references.

events.message: BIP 39: prettier formatting of implementation list

events.body: I updated my PR to also make the other languages look prettier :-)

By the way I specifically mention the wallet, because it provides an indication of how many bitcoin users depend on a BIP. I also added a link to the source code which could help in assessing if a BIP is fully or only partly implemented. In this case, it shows that the blockchain wallet currently doesn't use the passphrase (though it could), only the mnemonic words.
